reviewText:
I've seen Squishy's art on the internet for years and I have to say that this is some of Squishy's least appealing work.
Squishy really just does not have it anymore, not that Squishy ever really had it.
To get to the point, its not a very long one, its actually pretty dang short.

squishy does porno was a very interesting film indeed. as you can tell by the name it is about a girl named squishy and she gets into the porn film industry, but what you can't tell by the title is the brillant film making  that took place during this film.  all the pans, the zooms, and how a close  up of her eyes could tell you as much about the scene to come as a written  text.  also there were also many undertones and attempts to spoil the war  movement in vietnam but still full of love interests.  if you love good  movies and good porn, rent "squishy does porn".
